*arphicfonts-0.1 (27 June 2002)

  22 Aug 2002; Stuart Bouyer <stubear@gentoo.org> arphicfonts-0.1-r1.ebuild,
  files/CN-fonts.scale, files/TW-fonts.scale:

  Marko Daniel <mdaniel@soton.ac.uk> has updated the ebuild to install the
  fonts in their own directory and fixed a bug where the font encoding info
  wasn't being correctly produced for big5 and gb encodings. Closes bug 6281. 

  27 June 2002; Stuart Bouyer <stubear@gentoo.org> arphicfonts-0.1.ebuild:
  First ebuild added
